with Gloria.

00:18:05.570 --> 00:18:07.910 align:middle line:84%
And he said, we were
both very young.

00:18:07.910 --> 00:18:11.390 align:middle line:84%
She walked onto the stage
and the stagehand stopped,

00:18:11.390 --> 00:18:14.390 align:middle line:84%
and the director stopped, and
the other actors auditioning

00:18:14.390 --> 00:18:15.590 align:middle line:90%
stopped.

00:18:15.590 --> 00:18:17.620 align:middle line:84%
And he said,
Chantal, I don't know

00:18:17.620 --> 00:18:22.136 align:middle line:84%
how to tell you except she
had a presence about her.

00:18:22.136 --> 00:18:25.010 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I don't know
whether he remembers this,

00:18:25.010 --> 00:18:28.640 align:middle line:84%
but Tennessee Williams--
we were auditioning for--

00:18:28.640 --> 00:18:32.000 align:middle line:84%
and Tennessee was
the terror of actors

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:35.630 align:middle line:84%
because he would always
sit like in the second row

00:18:35.630 --> 00:18:42.710 align:middle line:84%
and he would talk throughout
the actors' auditions.

00:18:42.710 --> 00:18:44.900 align:middle line:84%
And that's really the
only thing I remember.

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:49.640 align:middle line:84%
So if he thought I had
presence dealing with that,

00:18:49.640 --> 00:18:50.990 align:middle line:90%
and he certainly did.

00:18:50.990 --> 00:18:53.926 align:middle line:90%
So but that's very, very funny.

00:18:53.926 --> 00:18:55.180 align:middle line:90%
>> I will remind him.

00:18:55.180 --> 00:18:59.620 align:middle line:84%
>> Tennessee really was,
he was just a terror.

00:18:59.620 --> 00:19:02.530 align:middle line:84%
He would always have somebody,
an assistant or something,

00:19:02.530 --> 00:19:04.820 align:middle line:84%
and he would be talking,
talking, talking, talking

00:19:04.820 --> 00:19:06.790 align:middle line:90%
through the audition.

00:19:06.790 --> 00:19:09.160 align:middle line:90%
>> Now you see what you've done?

00:19:09.160 --> 00:19:12.280 align:middle line:84%
You've successfully taken
the subject off of you

00:19:12.280 --> 00:19:15.460 align:middle line:90%
and your remarkable presence.

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:18.550 align:middle line:84%
What do you think it is
when someone has presence?

00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:26.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think you probably,
if you've got it, you know it.

00:19:26.980 --> 00:19:29.455 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, it
projects itself.

00:19:29.455 --> 00:19:32.920 align:middle line:90%


00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:34.930 align:middle line:84%
You know, there's
this wonderful thing

00:19:34.930 --> 00:19:40.010 align:middle line:84%
about Marilyn Monroe, which
I'm sure you've heard this,

00:19:40.010 --> 00:19:43.860 align:middle line:90%
but she could be--

00:19:43.860 --> 00:19:47.830 align:middle line:84%
I remember I had a party one
night and Marilyn was there.

00:19:47.830 --> 00:19:50.230 align:middle line:84%
And it was in the
days when she had

00:19:50.230 --> 00:19:52.120 align:middle line:84%
come to be in the Actors
Studio and all that.

00:19:52.120 --> 00:19:54.910 align:middle line:84%
And she was going around
without any makeup on.

00:19:54.910 --> 00:19:56.042 align:middle line:90%
And she came to the party.

00:19:56.042 --> 00:19:59.150 align:middle line:84%
And she had on a sort of
army-navy sweater and no makeup

00:19:59.150 --> 00:20:04.060 align:middle line:84%
and just a little
Vaseline on her eyelids.

00:20:04.060 --> 00:20:07.750 align:middle line:84%
And John Groth, the artist,
was coming to the party

00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:09.280 align:middle line:84%
