dying to meet her.

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:11.186 align:middle line:84%
So he arrived and he
said, where's Marilyn.

00:20:11.186 --> 00:20:12.560 align:middle line:84%
I said, she's out
on the terrace.

00:20:12.560 --> 00:20:16.352 align:middle line:84%
So he went out on
the terrace and there

00:20:16.352 --> 00:20:17.560 align:middle line:90%
were some other people there.

00:20:17.560 --> 00:20:21.010 align:middle line:84%
And she was out on the terrace
talking to Dick Avedon.

00:20:21.010 --> 00:20:24.340 align:middle line:84%
And he came back and he
said, no, she's not there.

00:20:24.340 --> 00:20:26.470 align:middle line:90%
And he didn't recognize her.

00:20:26.470 --> 00:20:27.520 align:middle line:90%
