Monroe and everybody

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:41.860 align:middle line:10%
would recognize her.

00:20:41.860 --> 00:20:44.080 align:middle line:84%
But if she didn't want
anybody to recognize her,

00:20:44.080 --> 00:20:46.935 align:middle line:84%
she could absolutely
fade into landscape.

00:20:46.935 --> 00:20:49.130 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:49.930 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:20:49.930 --> 00:20:52.060 align:middle line:84%
>> And I think it has
to happen up here,

